{"tid":1667150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察係狗，咁張建宗係咩？","createTime":"2019-10-21T10:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T10:06:44.000Z","uid":205394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b75e262b646a82284f704d340bba1694efcd14","tid":1667150,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"成件事以黎，D狗都係咁撚鳩張建宗<br />\n<br />\n堂堂政務司司長，一人之下萬人之上既位置<br />\n比一班狗係咁撚黎撚去<br />\n出黎講少少野都要比班狗傳召去解話<br />\n重要睇班狗收唔收貨<br />\n有咩事重想推佢出黎頂<br />\n<br />\n就算係盧偉聰呢個警長<br />\n實際上官位都比佢低<br />\n比狗撚既張建宗究竟算係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果狗係condom <br />\n佢係condom入面d精?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb01cf6fb23f5d0c8b0d5944f01283b294ac64e2","tid":1667150,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:03:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd81ce99bd3d229b23d9d2fb1e970b38590f4698","tid":1667150,"uid":15605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eb01cf6fb23f5d0c8b0d5944f01283b294ac64e2","tid":1667150,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:03:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCfnPDy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCfnPDy.jpg&h=47ab3621&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}